title: Bobby Brings His Wedding Performer Brittney Spencer In Studio + Lunchbox Tries To Buy George Strait’s House + Bobby Feud: Once A Week Things
itunes:title: Bobby Brings His Wedding Performer Brittney Spencer In Studio + Lunchbox Tries To Buy George Strait’s House + Bobby Feud: Once A Week Things
description:
Bobby brings in new artist Brittney Spencer who is going to perform at his wedding as Caitlin walks down the aisle. She performs one of her songs and an amazing cover! We saw that George Strait’s home in San Antonio is up for sale. So Lunchbox called and tried to buy it…using George Strait lyrics of course. We play a round of the Bobby Feud on things that only happen once a week! 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
